summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; providing for the acquisition of right-of-way necessary for the opening and establishing of College Way North from the intersection of Burke Avenue North and North 95th Street to Wallingford Avenue North at a point approximately midway between North 90th Street and North 92nd Street in the vicinity of North Seattle Community College and for the necessary expenses of the Law and Engineering Departments in connection with such purchase or any subsequent condemnation proceedings, and making an appropriation from the Arterial Development Fund therefor.
